-<case>

<id>C23</id>

<title>Edit button is displaed</title>

<template>Test Case (Text)</template>

<type>Functional</type>

<priority>Medium</priority>

<estimate/>

<references>TAS-19</references>


-<custom>


-<automation_type>

<id>0</id>

<value> None</value>

</automation_type>

<steps>Open the app. Click on New Task quick access button. Fill-in the information in the fields Push the Create button Push the Edit button from Done, In Progress and Open board </steps>

<expected>Verify the Create Task page is opened. Fill-in the given information and push Create button. The Task Board page is opened and different boards Done, In Progress and Open are displayed.Edit button should be displayed too.</expected>

</custom>

